Cook rice or noodles according to package directions. Drain pineapple, reserving 2 tablespoons juice. Stir together reserved pineapple juice, maple syrup and cornstarch in large skillet. Cook and stir until thickened and bubbly, cook and stir 2 minutes more. Stir in beans, ham and pineapple. Heat through. Serve over rice or noodles.